What is Amplience?\b0\par
Amplience is an API-first, headless content management platform for enterprise retail, enabling teams to do more, better, faster.\par
\b What are editions and event in Amplience?\b0\par
\b Event\b0 :- Events are created from the scheduling view.\line Events have start and end date that cover all the activity for the entire campaign.\line The event can also contain an attachment, which is specified as a URL.\line Within events we will create one or more editions, which represent a drop of content.\par
\b Editions\b0 :- Editions are what combine the "Drops" of content with the date it is sheduled to go live.\par
\b Slots\b0 :- Slots represent areas of your website,mobile site or app.\line They are used to determined where your content should bedelivered to.\par
